<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            /* Color System */
            --bg-primary: #0a0e27;
            --bg-secondary: #1a1f3a;
            --surface: rgba(26, 31, 58, 0.6);

            /* Gradients */
            --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #ec4899 50%, #6366f1 100%);
            --gradient-success: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            --gradient-warning: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #ea580c 100%);
            --gradient-danger: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            --gradient-info: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4 0%, #3b82f6 100%);

            /* Status Colors */
            --color-success: #10b981;
            --color-warning: #f59e0b;
            --color-danger: #ef4444;
            --color-info: #06b6d4;

            /* Text */
            --text-primary: #f9fafb;
            --text-secondary: #d1d5db;
            --text-tertiary: #9ca3af;

            /* Shadows */
            --shadow-sm: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            --shadow-md: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);

            /* Spacing */
            --spacing-xs: 8px;
            --spacing-sm: 12px;
            --spacing-md: 16px;
            --spacing-lg: 24px;
            --spacing-xl: 32px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Dark mode support */
        body.dark {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
        }

        /* Animated background grid */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1920px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
            padding: var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-lg);
            background: var(--surface);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            animation: slideDown 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            animation: pulse 3s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            }
            50% {
                box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
            }
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-tertiary);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-left: 60px;
        }

        .header-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .search-bar {
            position: relative;
        }

        .search-bar input {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 20px 12px 44px;

            width: 300px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;

        .notification-btn, .profile-btn {
            width: 44px;

            justify-content: center;

            height: 20px;

            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
            }
        }

        /* Stats Grid */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: var(--spacing-lg);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        .stat-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
        }

        .stat-card.success::before {
            background: var(--gradient-success);
        }

        .stat-card.warning::before {
            background: var(--gradient-warning);
        }

        .stat-card.danger::before {
            background: var(--gradient-danger);
        }

        .stat-card.info::before {
            background: var(--gradient-info);
        }

        .stat-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-primary) 0%, var(--text-secondary) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .stat-trend {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .stat-trend.up {
            color: var(--color-success);
        }

        .stat-trend.down {
            color: var(--color-danger);
        }

        /* Main Content Grid */
        .main-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
            gap: var(--spacing-lg);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        /* Glass Card */
        .glass-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .glass-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1), transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .live-indicator {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--color-success);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: livePulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes livePulse {
            0%, 100% {
                opacity: 1;
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.7);
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 0.7;
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0);
            }
        }

        /* Activity Feed */
        .activity-feed {
            max-height: 600px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-right: 8px;
        }

        .activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }

        .activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .activity-feed::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
        }

        .activity-item {
            padding: var(--spacing-sm);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            animation: slideInLeft 0.5s ease-out;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .activity-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);

        }

        .activity-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;

        .activity-amount {

        .activity-details {

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;

        .status-badge.approved {

        @keyframes alertPulse {

                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
            }
            50% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0);
            }
        }

        /* Transaction Table */
        .transaction-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 0 8px;
        }

        .transaction-table thead th {
            text-align: left;

        .user-cell {

            if (event.matches) {
                document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');

        // Mock data
        const merchants = ['Amazon', 'Netflix', 'Apple Store', 'Steam', 'PayPal', 'Stripe', 'Shopify', 'eBay', 'Etsy', 'Best Buy'];
        const users = ['John Doe', 'Jane Smith', 'Mike Johnson', 'Sarah Williams', 'David Brown', 'Emily Davis', 'Chris Wilson', 'Lisa Anderson'];
        const statuses = ['approved', 'blocked', 'review'];
        const statusIcons = { approved: 'âœ“', blocked: 'âœ•', review: 'â±' };

        let currentFilter = 'all';
        let transactions = [];

        // Generate random transaction
        function generateTransaction() {
            const status = statuses[Math.floor(Math.random() * statuses.length * (Math.random() > 0.85 ? 1 : 0.3))];
            const riskScore = status === 'blocked' ? Math.floor(Math.random() * 30 + 70) :
                             status === 'review' ? Math.floor(Math.random() * 40 + 30) :
                             Math.floor(Math.random() * 30);

            return {
                id: Date.now() + Math.random(),
                user: users[Math.floor(Math.random() * users.length)],
                amount: (Math.random() * 5000 + 10).toFixed(2),
                merchant: merchants[Math.floor(Math.random() * merchants.length)],
                risk: riskScore,
                status: status,
                time: new Date(),
                location: ['New York, US', 'London, UK', 'Tokyo, JP', 'Sydney, AU'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 4)],
                device: ['iPhone 14', 'Samsung Galaxy', 'iPad Pro', 'MacBook Pro'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 4)],
                ip: `${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}.${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}.${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}.${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}`
            };
        }

        // Initialize transactions
        for (let i = 0; i < 15; i++) {
            transactions.push(generateTransaction());
        }

        // Format time ago
        function timeAgo(date) {
            const seconds = Math.floor((new Date() - date) / 1000);
            if (seconds < 60) return `${seconds}s ago`;
            if (seconds < 3600) return `${Math.floor(seconds / 60)}m ago`;
            if (seconds < 86400) return `${Math.floor(seconds / 3600)}h ago`;
            return `${Math.floor(seconds / 86400)}d ago`;
        }

        // Render activity feed
        function renderActivityFeed() {
            const feed = document.getElementById('activityFeed');
            const recent = transactions.slice(0, 10);

            feed.innerHTML = recent.map(tx => `
                <div class="activity-item" onclick="showTransactionDetail(${tx.id})">
                    <div class="activity-header">
                        <div class="activity-amount">$${tx.amount}</div>
                        <div class="activity-time">${timeAgo(tx.time)}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="activity-details">
                        ${tx.user} â†’ ${tx.merchant}
                    </div>
                    <span class="status-badge ${tx.status}">${statusIcons[tx.status]} ${tx.status.toUpperCase()}</span>
                </div>
            `).join('');
        }

        // Render transaction table
        function renderTransactionTable() {
            const tbody = document.getElementById('transactionTableBody');
            const filtered = currentFilter === 'all' ? transactions : transactions.filter(tx => tx.status === currentFilter);

            tbody.innerHTML = filtered.map(tx => {
                const riskClass = tx.risk < 30 ? 'low' : tx.risk < 60 ? 'medium' : 'high';
                const initial = tx.user.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('');

                return `
                    <tr onclick="showTransactionDetail(${tx.id})">
                        <td>
                            <div class="user-cell">
                                <div class="user-avatar">${initial}</div>
                                <span>${tx.user}</span>
                            </div>
                        </td>

            const decisions = document.getElementById('mlDecisions');

    <script>
        // Dark mode detection

        // Mock data

        // Generate random transaction
        function generateTransaction() {
            const status = statuses[Math.floor(Math.random() * statuses.length * (Math.random() > 0.85 ? 1 : 0.3))];
            const riskScore = status === 'blocked' ? Math.floor(Math.random() * 30 + 70) :

                             Math.floor(Math.random() * 30);

            return {
                id: Date.now() + Math.random(),
                user: users[Math.floor(Math.random() * users.length)],
                amount: (Math.random() * 5000 + 10).toFixed(2),
                merchant: merchants[Math.floor(Math.random() * merchants.length)],
                risk: riskScore,
                status: status,
                time: new Date(),
                location: ['New York, US', 'London, UK', 'Tokyo, JP', 'Sydney, AU'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 4)],
                device: ['iPhone 14', 'Samsung Galaxy', 'iPad Pro', 'MacBook Pro'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 4)],
                ip: `${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}.${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}.${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}.${Math.floor(Math.random() * 255)}`
            };
        }

        // Initialize transactions
        for (let i = 0; i < 15; i++) {
            transactions.push(generateTransaction());
        }

        // Format time ago
        function timeAgo(date) {
            const seconds = Math.floor((new Date() - date) / 1000);
            if (seconds < 60) return `${seconds}s ago`;
            if (seconds < 3600) return `${Math.floor(seconds / 60)}m ago`;
            if (seconds < 86400) return `${Math.floor(seconds / 3600)}h ago`;
            return `${Math.floor(seconds / 86400)}d ago`;
        }

        // Render activity feed
        function renderActivityFeed() {
            const feed = document.getElementById('activityFeed');
            const recent = transactions.slice(0, 10);

            feed.innerHTML = recent.map(tx => `
                <div class="activity-item" onclick="showTransactionDetail(${tx.id})">
                    <div class="activity-header">
                        <div class="activity-amount">$${tx.amount}</div>
                        <div class="activity-time">${timeAgo(tx.time)}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="activity-details">
                        ${tx.user} â†’ ${tx.merchant}
                    </div>
                    <span class="status-badge ${tx.status}">${statusIcons[tx.status]} ${tx.status.toUpperCase()}</span>
                </div>
            `).join('');
        }

        // Render transaction table
        function renderTransactionTable() {
            const tbody = document.getElementById('transactionTableBody');
            const filtered = currentFilter === 'all' ? transactions : transactions.filter(tx => tx.status === currentFilter);

            tbody.innerHTML = filtered.map(tx => {
                const riskClass = tx.risk < 30 ? 'low' : tx.risk < 60 ? 'medium' : 'high';
                const initial = tx.user.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('');

                return `
                    <tr onclick="showTransactionDetail(${tx.id})">
                        <td>
                            <div class="user-cell">
                                <div class="user-avatar">${initial}</div>
                                <span>${tx.user}</span>

            const decisions = document.getElementById('mlDecisions');

                closeNotificationModal();

        // Add new transaction every 5 seconds
        setInterval(() => {
            transactions.unshift(generateTransaction());
            if (transactions.length > 50) transactions.pop();
            renderActivityFeed();
            if (currentFilter === 'all') renderTransactionTable();
            renderMLDecisions();

            // Update stats
            const blocked = transactions.filter(t => t.status === 'blocked').length;
            const review = transactions.filter(t => t.status === 'review').length;
            const total = transactions.length;
            const fraudRate = ((blocked / total) * 100).toFixed(2);

            document.getElementById('blockedTransactions').textContent = blocked.toLocaleString();

        renderActivityFeed();

        // Animate numbers on load
        function animateNumber(element, start, end, duration) {
            const range = end - start;
            const increment = range / (duration / 16);
            let current = start;

            const timer = setInterval(() => {
                current += increment;
                if ((increment > 0 && current >= end) || (increment < 0 && current <= end)) {
                    element.textContent = end.toLocaleString();
                    clearInterval(timer);
                } else {
                    element.textContent = Math.floor(current).toLocaleString();
                }
            }, 16);
        }

        window.addEventListener('load', () => {

                renderMLDecisions();
                renderAllTransactionsTable();
                closeModal();
            }
        }

        function blockTransaction(id) {
            const tx = transactions.find(t => t.id === id);
            if (tx) {
                tx.status = 'blocked';
                renderActivityFeed();
                renderTransactionTable();
                renderMLDecisions();
                renderAllTransactionsTable();
                closeModal();
            }

        document.getElementById('transactionModal').addEventListener('click', (e) => {

        document.getElementById('notificationModal').addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            if (e.target.classList.contains('modal')) {
                closeNotificationModal();
            }
        });

        // Add new transaction every 5 seconds
        setInterval(() => {

            renderActivityFeed();
            if (currentFilter === 'all') renderTransactionTable();
            renderMLDecisions();
            renderAllTransactionsTable();

            // Update stats
            const blocked = transactions.filter(t => t.status === 'blocked').length;
            const review = transactions.filter(t => t.status === 'review').length;
            const total = transactions.length;
            const fraudRate = ((blocked / total) * 100).toFixed(2);

            document.getElementById('blockedTransactions').textContent = blocked.toLocaleString();
            document.getElementById('underReview').textContent = review.toLocaleString();
            document.getElementById('fraudRate').textContent = fraudRate + '%';

        document.getElementById('startDate').valueAsDate = lastWeek;
        document.getElementById('endDate').valueAsDate = today;

        // Animate numbers on load
        function animateNumber(element, start, end, duration) {
            const range = end - start;
            const increment = range / (duration / 16);
            let current = start;

            const timer = setInterval(() => {
                current += increment;
                if ((increment > 0 && current >= end) || (increment < 0 && current <= end)) {
                    element.textContent = end.toLocaleString();
                    clearInterval(timer);
                } else {
                    element.textContent = Math.floor(current).toLocaleString();
                }
            }, 16);
        }

        // Animate stats on load
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
            animateNumber(document.getElementById('totalTransactions'), 0, 147382, 1500);
            animateNumber(document.getElementById('blockedTransactions'), 0, 1247, 1500);
            animateNumber(document.getElementById('underReview'), 0, 423, 1500);
        });
